      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable new-to-you ride? I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s in really great shape! It\u2019s been well-loved and runs beautifully\u2014perfect for daily commutes or your next weekend getaway. It\u2019s got plenty of life left in it and is just waiting for a new home. Come check it out and take it for a spin; you're going to love how it handles!",
