    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six. This high-revving power unit utilizes six individual throttle bodies and dual VANOS variable valve timing to deliver linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Power is channeled through a precise 6-speed manual gearbox to a GKN variable M-differential. The chassis remains taut with upgraded bushings and documented subframe reinforcement, ensuring structural integrity under high lateral loads. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with spirited use, the drivetrain remains robust with recent valve adjustments and rod bearing preventative maintenance completed. A visceral, analog driving experience for the discerning purist.",
